'''伦敦商学院'''（[[英语|英语]]：'''London Business School'''），简称'''LBS'''，是一所坐落于[[英国|英国]][[伦敦|伦敦]]市中心的国际化[[商学院|商学院]]，紧邻[[伦敦御苑|伦敦御苑]]之一的[[摄政公园|摄政公园]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=London|url=https://www.london.edu/about/our-campuses/london|access-date=2022-05-16|work=London Business School|language=en|archive-date=2022-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220516203307/https://www.london.edu/about/our-campuses/london}}</ref>，为[[倫敦大學|伦敦大学]]联邦的成员机构之一<ref>{{Cite web|title=London Business School|url=https://london.ac.uk/ways-study/study-campus-london/member-institutions/london-business-school|access-date=2022-05-16|work=University of London|language=en|archive-date=2021-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211121210206/https://london.ac.uk/ways-study/study-campus-london/member-institutions/london-business-school}}</ref>。LBS创办于1964年，是全球著名的商学院之一，也是英国成立最早的两所商学院之一（另一所为[[曼徹斯特商學院|曼彻斯特商学院]]）<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=BUSINESS SCHOOLS (MANCHESTER AND LONDON UNIVERSITIES) (Hansard, 11 May 1964)|url=https://api.parliament.uk/historic-hansard/commons/1964/may/11/business-schools-manchester-and-london|access-date=2022-05-16|work=api.parliament.uk}}</ref>。2007年，学院在[[阿拉伯联合酋长国|阿联酋]][[杜拜|迪拜]]设立了海外分校，专门为企业高管提供[[工商管理碩士|EMBA]]及其它定制化培训课程<ref name=":2">{{Cite web|title=Dubai|url=https://www.london.edu/about/our-campuses/dubai|access-date=2022-05-16|work=London Business School|language=en|archive-date=2022-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220516203306/https://www.london.edu/about/our-campuses/dubai}}</ref>。该校已通过商学院“[[商学院三重认证|三皇冠]]”（[[國際商管學院促進協會|AACSB]]/[[歐洲質量改善系統|EQUIS]]/[[工商管理硕士协会|AMBA]]）认证<ref>{{Cite web|title=Rankings and accreditation|url=https://www.london.edu/about/london-business-school/rankings-and-accreditation|access-date=2022-05-16|work=London Business School|language=en|archive-date=2022-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220217001634/https://www.london.edu/about/london-business-school/rankings-and-accreditation}}</ref>。

伦敦商学院历来被认为是[[欧洲|欧洲]]乃至全球最顶尖的商学院之一<ref>{{Cite journal |title=London Business School |url=https://www.economist.com/whichmba/london-business-school/2011 |journal=The Economist |issn=0013-0613 |access-date=2022-05-16 |archive-date=2022-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220516223114/https://www.economist.com/whichmba/london-business-school/2011 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=LBS recognised again as a leading European business school|url=https://www.london.edu/news/lbs-recognised-again-as-a-leading-european-business-school-1991|access-date=2022-05-16|work=London Business School|language=en|archive-date=2022-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220516223114/https://www.london.edu/news/lbs-recognised-again-as-a-leading-european-business-school-1991}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=清华大学-伦敦商学院金融硕士双学位项目签约仪式举行-清华大学|url=https://www.tsinghua.edu.cn/info/1178/29047.htm|access-date=2022-05-16|work=www.tsinghua.edu.cn}}</ref>。2021年，LBS旗下的[[工商管理碩士|MBA]]项目在《[[金融時報_(英國)|金融时报]]》全球商学院排行榜中位列世界第二，仅次于[[欧洲工商管理学院|欧洲工商管理学院]]（INSEAD）<ref>{{Cite web|title=Global MBA Ranking 2021 - Business school rankings from the Financial Times - FT.com|url=https://rankings.ft.com/rankings/2859/global-mba-ranking-2021|access-date=2022-05-16|work=rankings.ft.com|archive-date=2022-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220513114834/https://rankings.ft.com/rankings/2859/global-mba-ranking-2021}}</ref>，而该校的[[金融碩士|金融学硕士]]项目则连续多年被评为世界第一<ref>{{Cite web|title=Business school rankings from the Financial Times - FT.com|url=https://rankings.ft.com/home/masters-in-finance|access-date=2022-05-16|work=rankings.ft.com|archive-date=2022-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220523063915/http://rankings.ft.com/home/masters-in-finance}}</ref>。根据[[QS世界大学学科排名|QS世界大学学科排名]]，LBS的[[商科|商科]]教育于2015~2022年连续八年稳居世界前三<ref>{{Cite web|title=London Business School|url=https://www.topuniversities.com/universities/london-business-school|access-date=2022-05-16|work=Top Universities|language=en|archive-date=2022-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220417161210/https://www.topuniversities.com/universities/london-business-school}}</ref>，其[[金融学|金融学]]与[[管理学|管理学]]硕士项目亦高居全球前二<ref>{{Cite web|title=Business Masters - Masters in Finance 2022|url=https://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/business-masters-rankings/finance/2022|access-date=2022-05-16|work=Top Universities|language=en|archive-date=2022-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220428033728/https://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/business-masters-rankings/finance/2022}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Business Masters - Masters in Management 2022|url=https://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/business-masters-rankings/management/2022|access-date=2022-05-16|work=Top Universities|language=en|archive-date=2021-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211203053853/https://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/business-masters-rankings/management/2022}}</ref>。根据2018年度[[泰晤士高等教育世界大學排名|泰晤士高等教育世界大学排名]]，LBS在[[商學|商学]]与[[经济学|经济学]]领域位居世界第四，高于[[剑桥大学|剑桥大学]]和[[芝加哥大学|芝加哥大学]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=World University Rankings 2018 by subject: business and economics|url=https://www.timeshighereducation.com/world-university-rankings/2018/subject-ranking/business-and-economics|access-date=2022-05-16|date=2017-09-12|work=Times Higher Education (THE)|language=en|archive-date=2017-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171018012526/https://www.timeshighereducation.com/world-university-rankings/2018/subject-ranking/business-and-economics}}</ref>。2019年度《金融时报》全英商学院排名前六位分别是：伦敦商学院、[[牛津大学赛德商学院|牛津大学赛德商学院]]、[[賈吉商學院|剑桥大学贾奇商学院]]、[[華威商學院|华威商学院]]、[[帝国理工学院|帝国理工商学院]]以及[[貝氏商學院|贝叶斯商学院]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=European Business School Rankings 2019 - Business school rankings from the Financial Times - FT.com|url=https://rankings.ft.com/rankings/2836/european-business-school-rankings-2019|access-date=2022-05-16|work=rankings.ft.com|archive-date=2022-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220510001159/https://rankings.ft.com/rankings/2836/european-business-school-rankings-2019}}</ref>。

伦敦商学院不提供[[本科教育|本科教育]]，只开设有金融学和管理学相关的[[硕士|硕士]]、[[博士|博士]]项目<ref>{{Cite web|title=FAQs|url=https://www.london.edu/about/contact/faqs|access-date=2022-05-16|work=London Business School|language=en|archive-date=2022-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220516203307/https://www.london.edu/about/contact/faqs}}</ref>。除了其久负盛名的[[工商管理碩士|工商管理硕士]]（MBA和EMBA）项目<ref>{{Cite web|title=MBA {{!}} London Business School|url=https://www.london.edu/masters-degrees/mba|access-date=2022-05-16|work=www.london.edu|archive-date=2022-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220516233236/http://www.london.edu/masters-degrees/mba}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Executive MBA London {{!}} EMBA {{!}} London Business School|url=https://www.london.edu/masters-degrees/executive-mba-london|access-date=2022-05-16|work=www.london.edu|archive-date=2022-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220516203304/https://www.london.edu/masters-degrees/executive-mba-london}}</ref>，学院也为拥有长期工作经验的商业人士提供斯隆合作课程（Sloan Fellowship Programme）<ref>{{Cite web|title=LBS Sloan Masters in Leadership and Strategy {{!}} London Business School|url=https://www.london.edu/masters-degrees/sloan-masters-in-leadership-and-strategy|access-date=2022-05-16|work=www.london.edu|archive-date=2019-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190806212703/https://www.london.edu/masters-degrees/sloan-masters-in-leadership-and-strategy}}</ref>、金融硕士课程（Masters in Finance，MiF，为有长期金融机构工作经验的专业人士设立）<ref>{{Cite web|title=Masters in Finance Full-time {{!}} London Business School|url=https://www.london.edu/masters-degrees/masters-in-finance-full-time|access-date=2022-05-16|work=www.london.edu|archive-date=2022-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220516213431/https://www.london.edu/masters-degrees/masters-in-finance-full-time}}</ref>以及博士课程（PhD）<ref>{{Cite web|title=PhD|url=https://www.london.edu/phd|access-date=2022-05-16|work=London Business School|language=en|archive-date=2022-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220516203308/https://www.london.edu/phd}}</ref>。至于那些工作经验较少（两年以下）的优秀本科毕业生，学校则针对他们开设了[[管理硕士|管理硕士]]（Masters in Management，MiM）<ref>{{Cite web|title=Masters in Management {{!}} London Business School|url=https://www.london.edu/masters-degrees/masters-in-management|access-date=2022-05-16|work=www.london.edu|archive-date=2022-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220516203310/https://www.london.edu/masters-degrees/masters-in-management}}</ref>、金融分析硕士（Masters in Financial Analysis，MFA）<ref>{{Cite web|title=Masters in Financial Analysis {{!}} London Business School|url=https://www.london.edu/masters-degrees/masters-in-financial-analysis|access-date=2022-05-16|work=www.london.edu|archive-date=2022-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220422123136/https://www.london.edu/masters-degrees/masters-in-financial-analysis}}</ref>和商业分析与管理硕士（Masters in Analytics and Management，MAM）<ref>{{Cite web|title=Masters in Analytics and Management {{!}} London Business School|url=https://www.london.edu/masters-degrees/masters-in-analytics-and-management|access-date=2022-05-16|work=www.london.edu|archive-date=2022-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220516203306/https://www.london.edu/masters-degrees/masters-in-analytics-and-management}}</ref>等教学项目。学院还与[[哥伦比亚大学|哥伦比亚大学]]、[[香港大學|香港大学]]、[[清华大学|北京清华大学]]以及[[复旦大学|复旦大学]]等国际知名高校建立了紧密的合作关系，共同开办双学位课程<ref>{{Cite web|title=Home|url=https://www.emba-global.com/|access-date=2022-05-16|work=EMBA-Global|language=en-GB|archive-date=2022-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220507150840/https://www.emba-global.com/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=EMBA-Global Asia {{!}} Taught Postgraduate Admissions {{!}} The University of Hong Kong|url=https://admissions.hku.hk/tpg/programme/emba-global-asia|access-date=2022-05-16|work=admissions.hku.hk|archive-date=2022-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220407135216/https://admissions.hku.hk/tpg/programme/emba-global-asia}}</ref><ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=Global Masters in Management {{!}} London Business School|url=https://www.london.edu/masters-degrees/global-masters-in-management|access-date=2022-05-16|work=www.london.edu|archive-date=2022-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220516203303/https://www.london.edu/masters-degrees/global-masters-in-management}}</ref>。

伦敦商学院的录取流程极为严格，为全英申请难度最高的商学院之一<ref>{{Cite web|title=How difficult is it to get into LBS?|url=https://www.mbaandbeyond.com/blog/how-difficult-is-it-to-get-into-lbs|access-date=2022-05-16|work=MBA and Beyond|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210306051740/https://www.mbaandbeyond.com/blog/how-difficult-is-it-to-get-into-lbs}}</ref>。该校MBA项目获录取学生（2023届）的[[GMAT|GMAT]]平均成绩为708分<ref>{{Cite web|title=FAQs {{!}} MBA|url=https://www.london.edu/masters-degrees/mba/faqs|access-date=2022-05-16|work=London Business School|language=en|archive-date=2022-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220516203309/https://www.london.edu/masters-degrees/mba/faqs}}</ref>，与同属伦敦大学联盟体系的[[倫敦政治經濟學院|伦敦政治经济学院]]（LSE）相当<ref>{{Cite web|title=GRE and GMAT|url=https://www.lse.ac.uk/study-at-lse/Graduate/Prospective-students/Entry-requirements/GRE-and-GMAT.aspx|access-date=2022-05-16|last=LSE|first=London School of Economics and Political Science|work=London School of Economics and Political Science|language=en-GB}}</ref>。

==校史==
伦敦商学院创办于1964年，是英国成立最早的两所商学院之一（另一所为[[曼徹斯特商學院|曼彻斯特商学院]]）<ref name=":1" />。

伦敦商学院于2007年成立了[[杜拜|迪拜]]分校，专门为企业高阶主管提供[[工商管理碩士|EMBA]]及其它定制化培训课程<ref name=":2" />。
==排名声誉==
2011年，伦敦商学院连续第三年被英国《[[金融時報_(英國)|金融时报]]》全球商学院排行榜评为世界第一（与[[宾夕法尼亚大学沃顿商学院|宾夕法尼亚大学沃顿商学院]]并列第一）<ref>{{Cite web|title=2011 Financial Times Ranking of the Best B-Schools|url=https://poetsandquants.com/mba-rankings/wharton-london-tie-for-first-in-2011-financial-times-mba-ranking/|access-date=2022-05-16|date=2011-01-31|last=Byrne|first=John A.|work=Poets&Quants|language=en-US}}</ref>。学院在2012年与2013年发布的排名中被评为世界第四<ref>{{Cite web|title=Global MBA Rankings 2012 - Business school rankings from the Financial Times - FT.com|url=https://rankings.ft.com/rankings/1071/global-mba-rankings-2012|access-date=2022-05-16|work=rankings.ft.com|archive-date=2022-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220424145224/https://rankings.ft.com/rankings/1071/global-mba-rankings-2012}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Global MBA Ranking 2013 - Business school rankings from the Financial Times - FT.com|url=https://rankings.ft.com/rankings/1412/global-mba-ranking-2013|access-date=2022-05-16|work=rankings.ft.com|archive-date=2022-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220516224616/https://rankings.ft.com/rankings/1412/global-mba-ranking-2013}}</ref>，在2016年则回升至世界第三<ref>{{Cite web|title=Global MBA Ranking 2016 - Business school rankings from the Financial Times - FT.com|url=https://rankings.ft.com/rankings/2632/global-mba-ranking-2016|access-date=2022-05-16|work=rankings.ft.com|archive-date=2022-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220516224423/https://rankings.ft.com/rankings/2632/global-mba-ranking-2016}}</ref>。而在其它世界商学院排名中，伦敦商学院也长期稳居前十<ref>{{Cite web|title=QS World University Rankings by Subject 2015 - Business & Management Studies|url=https://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/university-subject-rankings/2015/business-management-studies|access-date=2022-05-16|work=Top Universities|language=en|archive-date=2022-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220213164056/https://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/university-subject-rankings/2015/business-management-studies}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title=These Are the Best International Business Schools|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/features/2016-best-international-business-schools/|newspaper=Bloomberg.com|accessdate=2022-05-16|language=en|archive-date=2022-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220327103241/https://www.bloomberg.com/features/2016-best-international-business-schools/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=London Business School Is The Best International Two-Year Business School For ROI|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/christinasettimi/2017/09/25/london-business-school-is-the-best-international-two-year-business-school-for-roi/|access-date=2022-05-16|last=Settimi|first=Christina|work=Forbes|language=en|archive-date=2022-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220516224416/https://www.forbes.com/sites/christinasettimi/2017/09/25/london-business-school-is-the-best-international-two-year-business-school-for-roi/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=University and business school ranking in United Kingdom|url=https://www.eduniversal-ranking.com/business-school-university-ranking-in-united-kingdom.html|access-date=2022-05-16|work=www.eduniversal-ranking.com|language=en|archive-date=2022-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220213184113/https://eduniversal-ranking.com/business-school-university-ranking-in-united-kingdom.html}}</ref>。

